description:
We'll be continuing our theme of "What did I miss?" and have two fantastic talks for you:

**Emily Cook - What did Vue miss? 3 Key Updates**
Of all of the great new updates that are part of Vue 3, this talk will focus on the following: Volar, Vite and Pinia.

**David Darnes - Building tabs in Web Components**
Sharing some of the processes and details that went into building a tab interface for our [Design System Nord](https://nordhealth.design)

\-\-\-
A huge thank you to our venue sponsor SR2 for hosting us and providing refreshments.
title: What did I miss? - Bristol JS - July 2022
